      "description": "No mobile-native reading system for long legal documents. Missing: 1) Floating Action Button (FAB) for quick TOC access/section jump, 2) Reading progress indicator (scroll percentage or section-based), 3) Resume reading position persistence (localStorage/session), 4) Share-at-position deep linking. Current implementation appears to be a static HTML renderer without affordances for 10,000+ word DOU documents on 6-inch screens. This is a production blocker for mobile-first legal research.",
